                  +button-icon('a', 'preview')(href="#")._border._border_bg-white._preview._wide.__button View this space page preview
                +col({ xl: 12, md: 6, sm: 12})
                  +space-info-text You can also get back to any of this sections in case of changing something:
                  +space-info-controls2
          +e.column_rborder._stretch._mr._md-mb80
            +e.subsection._mg64
              +section-title('h2')._mid50._mg24 Everything is fine. Now you are ready to publish your space on Space Pool
              +content-zone._max500
                p This is a last step of Space adding walktrough. Your space is now added to your Spaces. You can now add and manage rental offers in specified sections
            +e.subsection._mg64
              +section-title('h3')._mid._mg12 What to do next?
              +content-zone
                p Check all the information about your space If everything is okay publish the space
          +e.column_hints
            +grid.grid_layout.grid_t55
              +col({xl: 12, md: 6, sm: 12})
                +e.subsection
                  +section-title('h4')._mg28 Useful tip
                  +content-zone
                    p This is just a beggining! Please donâ€™t stop adding new rental offers for your places. If you have a rental offer with extra features you are always welcome to add it to your space.
              +col({xl: 12, md: 6, sm: 12})
                +e.subsection
                  +section-title('h4')._mg28 Example:
                  +content-zone
                    p <b>HOT DESK</b> and <b>HOT DESK with access to workshops and lectures</b> are to different rental offers with possibly two differenet prices. So you can always add a rental offer or same rental offer plus extra services.
        +form-panel._links._border
          +e.links
            +link-icon('select-arrow', 'a')(href="#")._back._bold._no-shadow.__button Back
          +button-icon('a', 'select-arrow')(href="#").__button_wide Publish this space


